\subsection{Method \code{get_withdrawal_history()}}{
Get Withdrawal History

Retrieves paginated withdrawal history with optional filtering by currency,
status, and time range. Automatically converts \code{created_at} timestamps
to POSIXct for convenient analysis.
\subsection{Workflow}{
\enumerate{
\item \strong{Pagination}: Uses \code{private$.paginate()} to fetch all pages of withdrawal records up to \code{max_pages}.
\item \strong{Flattening}: Combines all pages into a single \code{data.table} via \code{flatten_pages()}.
\item \strong{Timestamp Conversion}: Coerces \code{created_at} (milliseconds) to POSIXct in-place.
}
}

\subsection{API Endpoint}{

\verb{GET https://api.kucoin.com/api/v1/withdrawals}
}

\subsection{Official Documentation}{

\href{https://www.kucoin.com/docs-new/rest/account-info/withdrawals/get-withdrawal-history}{KuCoin Get Withdrawal History}

Verified: 2026-05-23
}

\subsection{Automated Trading Usage}{
\itemize{
\item \strong{Withdrawal Monitoring}: Poll for \code{"SUCCESS"} status to confirm funds have left the exchange.
\item \strong{Reconciliation}: Match \code{wallet_tx_id} against on-chain transaction hashes for audit.
\item \strong{Time-Windowed Queries}: Use \code{startAt}/\code{endAt} timestamps to retrieve withdrawals within a specific period.
}
}

